snippet.title: Gingerbread Dash! for Andoird
snippet.description:
Gingerbread Dash! is an Android game developed by Ateam Inc.
Gameplay consists of helping the Gingerbread Man runaway from the Giant Fox
without falling into the water or being caught by crows flying by.
The Gingerbread Man is controlled by tilting the Android device in the
desired direction, with greater tilt equaling greater movement speed.
